==English==
====Pronunciation====
*[[AHD]]: klō'zhûr

===Noun===
'''closure''' (''plural'': '''closures''')
# an event or occurence that signifies an ending
# a feeling of completeness; the experience of an emotional conclusion, usually to a difficult period
# {{computing}}: an [[abstraction]] that binds a function to the [[bound variable|bound variables]] within the function's [[scope]]
# {{mathematics}}: the smallest object that both includes the object as a subset and possesses some given property

